<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>{% include "court_base.css" %}</style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header-block">
        <strong>Date:</strong> {{ date_of_draft }}<br><br>
        <strong>To,</strong><br>
        The Commissioner,<br>
        Bruhat Bengaluru Mahanagara Palike (BBMP),<br>
        N.R. Square, Bengaluru – 560002,<br>
        Karnataka.
    </div>

    <div class="subject-line">
        SUBJECT: Request for Emergency Shelter Accommodation Under BBMP Urban Homeless Scheme
    </div>

    <div class="body-text">
        Respected Sir/Madam,
    </div>

    <div class="body-text">
        I, <strong>{{ applicant_name }}</strong>, hereby submit this request for emergency shelter accommodation under the Bruhat Bengaluru Mahanagara Palike's Urban Homeless Shelter Scheme.
    </div>

    <h2>Applicant Details</h2>
    <table>
        <tr><th>Full Name</th><td>{{ applicant_name }}</td></tr>
        <tr><th>Age</th><td>{{ applicant_age | default("") }}</td></tr>
        <tr><th>Previous Address</th><td>{{ property_address | default("") }}</td></tr>
        <tr><th>Contact Number</th><td>{{ applicant_phone | default("") }}</td></tr>
        <tr><th>Category</th><td>{{ caste_category | default("") }}</td></tr>
        <tr><th>Family Members</th><td>{{ family_members | default("") }}</td></tr>
    </table>

    <h2>Reason for Request</h2>
    <div class="body-text">
        {{ draft_body_summary }}
    </div>

    <div class="body-text">
        I am currently without any shelter and am in urgent need of safe accommodation. I do not have the financial means to arrange for alternative housing at this time.
    </div>

    <div class="body-text">
        I kindly request you to allot emergency shelter at the nearest BBMP night shelter or any available urban shelter under your jurisdiction.
    </div>

    <div class="body-text">
        I hereby declare that all the information furnished above is true and correct to the best of my knowledge.
    </div>

    <div class="date-place">
        <strong>Place:</strong> Bengaluru<br>
        <strong>Date:</strong> {{ date_of_draft }}
    </div>

    <div class="signature-block">
        <div class="line"></div>
        <strong>{{ applicant_name }}</strong><br>
        Applicant
    </div>
</body>
</html>
